title: Cattle Hide Leather in Process, Stocks in All Hands for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1920-1938 (2)--Original Data, 1939-1943. NBER Derived This Variable By Subtracting Figures For "Finished Stocks" From "Total In Process And Finished Stocks." Data Include Kip Sides Corrected To Equivalent Hides. Although Data Are Presented As Two Original And Two Seasonally Adjusted Variables, Data Are Comparable Throughout The Entire Time Span Of The Series. Source: NBER Computed This Variable From The New York Stock Exchange, "Monthly Statistical Supplement To The Weekly Market Report"

This NBER data series m05046b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 5 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter05.html.

NBER Indicator: m05046b
